install modules in linux machine
    boto3: AWS automation
    paramiko: connect ssh
    fabric: advance version of parameto (connected different server and extcute the tasks in diff servers)
    kubernets: for k8
    docker: for docker
    requests: call api request like curl command GET, PUT, DELETE and CREATE
    pyyaml: reading the yaml files
    pytest: for testing the code like unit test and function tests

